==English==
=== Noun ===
'''sexism''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#The treating of a person or people of one [[sex]] differently from others of the [[opposite sex]] based on assumptions or [[stereotype]]s relating to the sex of the person or people so treated; often, but not always, by a man or men towards a woman or women.
#:''We can't hire him as a kindergarten teacher. Men just don't understand children.''
#:''Girls are more mature than boys.''

